	(36853, 8, 0, 'Perish!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17008, 'Sindragosa - SAY_KILL 1'),
	(36853, 8, 1, 'A flaw of mortality...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17009, 'Sindragosa - SAY_KILL 2'),
	(36853, 9, 0, 'Enough! I tire of these games!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17011, 'Sindragosa - SAY_BERSERK'),
	(36853, 10, 0, 'Free...at last...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17010, 'Sindragosa - SAY_DEATH'),
	(36855, 0, 0, 'You have found your way here, because you are among the few gifted with true vision in a world cursed with blindness.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17272, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_1'),
	(36855, 1, 0, 'You can see through the fog that hangs over this world like a shroud, and grasp where true power lies.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17273, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_2'),
	(36855, 2, 0, 'Fix your eyes upon your crude hands: the sinew, the soft meat, the dark blood coursing within.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16878, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_3'),
	(36855, 3, 0, 'It is a weakness; a crippling flaw.... A joke played by the Creators upon their own creations.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17268, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_4'),
	(36855, 4, 0, 'The sooner you come to accept your condition as a defect, the sooner you will find yourselves in a position to transcend it.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17269, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_5'),
	(36855, 5, 0, 'Through our Master, all things are possible. His power is without limit, and his will unbending.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17270, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_6'),
	(36855, 6, 0, 'Those who oppose him will be destroyed utterly, and those who serve -- who serve wholly, unquestioningly, with utter devotion of mind and soul -- elevated to heights beyond your ken.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17271, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_INTRO_7'),
	(36855, 7, 0, 'What is this disturbance?! You dare trespass upon this hallowed ground? This shall be your final resting place.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16868, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_AGGRO'),
	(36855, 8, 0, 'Enough! I see I must take matters into my own hands!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16877, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_PHASE_2'),
	(36855, 9, 0, '%s\'s Mana Barrier shimmers and fades away!', 41, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_PHASE_2_EMOTE'),
	(36855, 10, 0, 'You are weak, powerless to resist my will!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16876, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_DOMINATE_MIND'),
	(36855, 11, 0, 'Take this blessing and show these intruders a taste of our master\'s power.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16873, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_DARK_EMPOWERMENT'),
	(36855, 12, 0, 'I release you from the curse of flesh!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16874, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_DARK_TRANSFORMATION'),
	(36855, 13, 0, 'Arise and exult in your pure form!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16875, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_ANIMATE_DEAD'),
	(36855, 14, 0, 'Do you yet grasp of the futility of your actions?', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16869, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_KILL_1'),
	(36855, 14, 1, 'Embrace the darkness... Darkness eternal!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16870, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_KILL_2'),
	(36855, 15, 0, 'This charade has gone on long enough.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16872, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_BERSERK'),
	(36855, 16, 0, 'All part of the masters plan! Your end is... inevitable!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16871, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_DEATH'),
	(36873, 0, 0, '%s attempts to run away in fear!', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'combat Flee'),
