	(29068, 31, 0, 'Think, $N. Think back. Try and remember the snow capped mountains o\' Dun Morogh! Ye were born there, $Glad:lass;. Remember the splendor o\' life, $N! Ye were a champion o\' the dwarves once! This isn\'t ye!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_THINK_5'),
