	(26530, 5, 2, 'Your flesh betrays you.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13482, 'salramm SAY_STEAL_FLESH_3'),
	(26530, 6, 0, 'Say hello to some friends of mine.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13476, 'salramm SAY_SUMMON_GHOULS_1'),
	(26530, 6, 1, 'Come, citizen of Stratholme! Meet your saviors.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 13477, 'salramm SAY_SUMMON_GHOULS_2'),
	(26499, 0, 0, 'Glad you could make it, Uther.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12828, 'culling SAY_PHASE101'),
	(26499, 1, 0, 'As if I could forget. Listen, Uther, there\'s something about the plague you should know...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12829, 'culling SAY_PHASE103'),
	(26499, 2, 0, 'Oh, no. We\'re too late. These people have all been infected! They may look fine now, but it\'s just a matter of time before they turn into the undead!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12830, 'culling SAY_PHASE104'),
	(26499, 3, 0, 'This entire city must be purged.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12831, 'culling SAY_PHASE106'),
	(26499, 4, 0, 'Damn it, Uther! As your future king, I order you to purge this city!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12832, 'culling SAY_PHASE108'),
	(26499, 5, 0, 'Then I must consider this an act of treason.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12833, 'culling SAY_PHASE110'),
	(26499, 6, 0, 'Have I? Lord Uther, by my right of succession and the sovereignty of my crown, I hereby relieve you of your command and suspend your paladins from service.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12834, 'culling SAY_PHASE112'),
	(26499, 7, 0, 'It\'s done! Those of you who have the will to save this land, follow me! The rest of you... get out of my sight!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12835, 'culling SAY_PHASE114'),
	(26499, 8, 0, 'Jaina?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12836, 'culling SAY_PHASE116'),
	(26499, 9, 0, 'Take position here, and I will lead a small force inside Stratholme to begin the culling. We must contain and purge the infected for the sake of all of Lordaeron!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14327, 'culling SAY_PHASE118'),
	(26499, 10, 0, 'Everyone looks ready. Remember, these people are all infected with the plague and will die soon. We must purge Stratholme to protect the remainder of Lordaeron from the Scourge. Let\'s go.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14293, 'culling SAY_PHASE201'),
	(26499, 11, 0, 'I can only help you with a clean death.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14294, 'culling SAY_PHASE203'),
	(26499, 12, 0, 'That was just the beginning.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14295, 'culling SAY_PHASE205'),
	(26499, 13, 0, 'I won\'t allow it, Mal\'Ganis! Better that these people die by my hand than serve as your slaves in death!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14296, 'culling SAY_PHASE208'),
	(26499, 14, 0, 'Mal\'ganis will send out some of his Scourge minions to interfere with us. Those of you with the strongest steel and magic shall go forth and destroy them. I will lead the rest of my forces in purging Stratholme of the infected.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14885, 'culling SAY_PHASE209'),
	(26499, 15, 0, 'Champions, meet me at the Town Hall at once. We must take the fight to Mal\'Ganis.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14297, 'culling SAY_PHASE210'),
	(26499, 16, 0, 'Follow me, I know the way through.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14298, 'culling SAY_PHASE301'),
	(26499, 17, 0, 'Yes, I\'m glad I could get to you before the plague.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14299, 'culling SAY_PHASE303'),
	(26499, 18, 0, 'What is this sorcery?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14300, 'culling SAY_PHASE304'),
	(26499, 19, 0, 'Mal\'Ganis appears to have more than scourge in his arsenal. We should make haste.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14301, 'culling SAY_PHASE306. NEEDS VERIFICATION'),
	(26499, 20, 0, 'More vile sorcery! Be ready for anything!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14302, 'culling SAY_PHASE307'),
	(26499, 21, 0, 'Let\'s move on.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14303, 'culling SAY_PHASE308'),
	(26499, 22, 0, 'Watch your backs: they have us surrounded in this hall.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14304, 'culling SAY_PHASE309'),
	(26499, 23, 0, 'One less obstacle to deal with.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'culling SAY_PHASE310. NEEDS VERIFICATION'),
	(26499, 24, 0, 'Mal\'Ganis is not making this easy.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14305, 'culling SAY_PHASE311'),
	(26499, 25, 0, 'They\'re very persistent.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14306, 'culling SAY_PHASE312'),
	(26499, 26, 0, 'What else can he put in my way?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14307, 'culling SAY_PHASE313'),
	(26499, 27, 0, 'I do what I must for Lordaeron, and neither your words nor your actions will stop me.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14309, 'culling SAY_PHASE315'),
	(26499, 28, 0, 'The quickest path to Mal\'Ganis lies behind that bookshelf ahead.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14308, 'culling SAY_PHASE401'),
	(26499, 29, 0, 'This will only take a moment.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14310, 'culling SAY_PHASE402'),
	(26499, 30, 0, 'I\'m relieved this secret passage still works.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14311, 'culling SAY_PHASE403'),
	(26499, 31, 0, 'Let\'s move through here as quickly as possible. If the undead don\'t kill us, the fires might.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14312, 'culling SAY_PHASE404'),
	(26499, 32, 0, 'Rest a moment and clear your lungs, but we must move again soon.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14313, 'culling SAY_PHASE405'),
	(26499, 33, 0, 'That\'s enough; we must move again. Mal\'Ganis awaits.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14314, 'culling SAY_PHASE406'),
	(26499, 34, 0, 'At last some good luck. Market Row has not caught fire yet. Mal\'Ganis is supposed to be in Crusaders\' Square, which is just ahead. Tell me when you\'re ready to move forward.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14315, 'culling SAY_PHASE407'),
	(26499, 35, 0, 'Justice will be done.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14316, 'culling SAY_PHASE501'),
	(26499, 36, 0, 'We\'re going to finish this right now, Mal\'Ganis. Just you... and me.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14317, 'culling SAY_PHASE502'),
	(26499, 37, 0, 'I\'ll hunt you to the ends of the earth if I have to! Do you hear me? To the ends of the earth!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14318, 'culling SAY_PHASE503'),
	(26499, 38, 0, 'You performed well this day. Anything that Mal\'Ganis has left behind is yours. Take it as your reward. I must now begin plans for an expedition to Northrend.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14319, 'culling SAY_PHASE504'),
	(26528, 0, 0, 'Watch your tone with me, boy. You may be the prince, but I\'m still your superior as a paladin!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12839, 'culling SAY_PHASE102'),
	(26528, 1, 0, 'What?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12840, 'culling SAY_PHASE105'),
	(26528, 2, 0, 'How can you even consider that? There\'s got to be some other way.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12841, 'culling SAY_PHASE107'),
	(26528, 3, 0, 'You are not my king yet, boy! Nor would I obey that command even if you were!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12842, 'culling SAY_PHASE109'),
	(26528, 4, 0, 'Treason? Have you lost your mind, Arthas?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12843, 'culling SAY_PHASE111'),
	(26528, 5, 0, 'You\'ve just crossed a terrible threshold, Arthas.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12844, 'culling SAY_PHASE115'),
	(26497, 0, 0, 'Arthas! You can\'t just--', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12837, 'culling SAY_PHASE113'),
	(26497, 1, 0, 'I\'m sorry, Arthas. I can\'t watch you do this.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 12838, 'culling SAY_PHASE117'),
	(28167, 0, 0, 'Prince Arthas, may the light be praised! Many people in the town have begun to fall seriously ill, can you help us?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'culling SAY_PHASE202'),
	(28169, 0, 0, 'What? This can\'t be!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'culling SAY_PHASE204'),
	(31126, 0, 0, 'Ah, you\'ve finally arrived Prince Arthas. You\'re here just in the nick of time.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'culling SAY_PHASE302'),
	(31126, 1, 0, 'There\'s no need for you to understand, Arthas. All you need to do is die.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'culling SAY_PHASE305'),
	(26533, 0, 0, 'Yes, this is the beginning. I\'ve been waiting for you, young prince. I am Mal\'Ganis.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14410, 'malganis SAY_INTRO_1 | culling SAY_PHASE206'),
	(26533, 1, 0, 'As you can see, your people are now mine. I will now turn this city household by household, until the flame of life has been snuffed out... forever.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14411, 'malganis SAY_INTRO_2 | culling SAY_PHASE207'),
	(26533, 2, 0, 'This will be a fine test...Prince Arthas...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14413, 'malganis SAY_AGGRO'),
	(26533, 3, 0, 'All too easy...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14416, 'malganis SAY_KILL_1'),
	(26533, 3, 1, 'The dark lord is displeased with your interference...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14417, 'malganis SAY_KILL_2'),
	(26533, 3, 2, 'It is Prince Arthas I want... not you...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14418, 'malganis SAY_KILL_3'),
	(26533, 4, 0, 'Anak\'Keri...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14422, 'malganis SAY_SLAY_1'),
	(26533, 4, 1, 'My onslaught will wash over the Lich King\'s forces...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14423, 'malganis SAY_SLAY_2'),
	(26533, 4, 2, 'Your death is in vain, tiny mortal...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14424, 'malganis SAY_SLAY_3'),
	(26533, 4, 3, 'Your time has come to an end!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14425, 'malganis SAY_SLAY_4'),
	(26533, 5, 0, 'Time out...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14414, 'malganis SAY_SLEEP_1'),
	(26533, 5, 1, 'You seem...tired...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14415, 'malganis SAY_SLEEP_2'),
	(26533, 6, 0, 'I spent too much time in that weak little shell...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14426, 'malganis SAY_30HEALTH'),
	(26533, 7, 0, '(Eredun) I AM MAL\'GANIS! I AM ETERNAL!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14427, 'malganis SAY_15HEALTH'),
	(26533, 8, 0, 'ENOUGH! I waste my time here...I must gather my strength on the home world...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14428, 'malganis SAY_ESCAPE_SPEECH_1'),
	(26533, 9, 0, 'You\'ll never defeat the Lich King without my forces! I\'ll have my revenge...on him, AND you...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14429, 'malganis SAY_ESCAPE_SPEECH_2'),
	(26533, 10, 0, 'Your journey has just begun, young prince. Gather your forces and meet me in the artic land of Northrend. It is there that we shall settle the score between us. It is there that your true destiny will unfold.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14412, 'malganis SAY_OUTRO'),
	(17879, 0, 0, 'Why do you aid the Magus? Just think of how many lives could be saved if the portal is never opened, if the resulting wars could be erased ...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10412, 'chrono lord deja SAY_ENTER'),
	(17879, 1, 0, 'If you will not cease this foolish quest, then you will die!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10414, 'chrono lord deja SAY_AGGRO'),
	(17879, 2, 0, 'You have outstayed your welcome, Timekeeper. Begone!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10413, 'chrono lord deja SAY_BANISH'),
	(17879, 3, 0, 'I told you it was a fool\'s quest!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10415, 'chrono lord deja SAY_SLAY1'),
	(17879, 3, 1, 'Leaving so soon?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10416, 'chrono lord deja SAY_SLAY2'),
	(17879, 4, 0, 'Time ... is on our side.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10417, 'chrono lord deja SAY_DEATH'),
	(17881, 0, 0, 'The time has come to shatter this clockwork universe forever! Let us no longer be slaves of the hourglass! I warn you: those who do not embrace the greater path shall become victims of its passing!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10400, 'aeonus SAY_ENTER'),
	(17881, 1, 0, 'Let us see what fate lays in store...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10402, 'aeonus SAY_AGGRO'),
	(17881, 2, 0, 'Your time is up, slave of the past!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10401, 'aeonus SAY_BANISH'),
	(17881, 3, 0, 'One less obstacle in our way!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10403, 'aeonus SAY_SLAY1'),
	(17881, 3, 1, 'No one can stop us! No one!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10404, 'aeonus SAY_SLAY2'),
	(17881, 4, 0, 'It is only a matter...of time.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10405, 'aeonus SAY_DEATH'),
	(17881, 5, 0, 'goes into a frenzy!', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'aeonus EMOTE_FRENZY'),
	(15608, 0, 0, 'The time has come! Gul\'dan, order your warlocks to double their efforts! Moments from now the gateway will open and your Horde will be released upon this ripe, unsuspecting world!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10435, 'medivh SAY_ENTER'),
	(15608, 1, 0, 'What is this? Champions, coming to my aid? I sense the hand of the dark one in this. Truly this sacred event bears his blessing?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10436, 'medivh SAY_INTRO'),
	(15608, 2, 0, 'Champions! My shield grows weak!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10437, 'medivh SAY_WEAK75'),
	(15608, 3, 0, 'My powers must be concentrated on the portal! I do not have time to hold the shield!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10438, 'medivh SAY_WEAK50'),
	(15608, 4, 0, 'The shield is nearly gone! All that I have worked for is in danger!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10439, 'medivh SAY_WEAK25'),
	(15608, 5, 0, 'No! Damn this feeble, mortal coil!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10441, 'medivh SAY_DEATH'),
	(15608, 6, 0, 'I am grateful for your aid, champions. Now, Gul\'dan\'s Horde will sweep across this world like a locust swarm, and all my designs, all my carefully-laid plans will at last fall into place.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10440, 'medivh SAY_WIN'),
	(15608, 7, 0, 'Orcs of the Horde! This portal is the gateway to your new destiny! Azeroth lies before you, ripe for the taking!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'medivh SAY_ORCS_ENTER'),
	(15608, 8, 0, 'Gul\'dan speaks the truth! We should return at once to tell our brothers of the news! Retreat back trought the portal!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'medivh SAY_ORCS_ANSWER'),
	(17880, 0, 0, 'Why do you persist? Surely you can see the futility of it all. It is not too late! You may still leave with your lives ...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10442, 'temporus SAY_ENTER'),
	(17880, 1, 0, 'So be it ... you have been warned.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10444, 'temporus SAY_AGGRO'),
	(17880, 2, 0, 'Time... sands of time is run out for you.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10443, 'temporus SAY_BANISH'),
	(17880, 3, 0, 'You should have left when you had the chance.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10445, 'temporus SAY_SLAY1'),
	(17880, 3, 1, 'Your days are done.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10446, 'temporus SAY_SLAY2'),
	(17880, 4, 0, 'My death means ... little.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 10447, 'temporus SAY_DEATH'),
	(23002, 0, 0, 'You, there! Hand over that moonstone and nobody gets hurt!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'sprysprocket SAY_START'),
	(23002, 1, 0, 'Just chill!', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'sprysprocket SAY_WHISPER_CHILL'),
	(23002, 2, 0, 'All right, you win! I surrender! Just don\'t hurt me!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'sprysprocket SAY_END'),
	(23002, 3, 0, '%s takes the Southfury moonstone and escapes into the river. Follow her!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'sprysprocket EMOTE_START'),
	(3568, 0, 0, 'Mist! I feared I would never see you again! Yes, I am well, do not worry for me. You must rest and recover your health.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'mist SAY_AT_HOME'),
	(3568, 1, 0, '%s growls in acknowledgement before straightening and making her way off into the forest.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'mist EMOTE_AT_HOME'),
	(15381, 0, 0, 'We must act quickly or all shall be lost!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_1'),
	(15381, 1, 0, 'NOW, STAGHELM! WE GO NOW! Prepare your magic!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_2'),
	(15381, 2, 0, 'Stay close...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_3'),
	(15381, 3, 0, 'The sands of time will halt, but only for a moment! I will now conjure the barrier.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_4'),
	(15381, 4, 0, 'FINISH THE SPELL STAGHELM! I CANNOT HOLD THE GLYPHS OF WARDING IN PLACE MUCH LONGER! CALL FORTH THE ROOTS!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_5'),
	(15381, 5, 0, 'It... It is over, Lord Staghelm. We are victorious. Albeit the cost for this victory was great.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_6'),
	(15381, 6, 0, 'There is but one duty that remains...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_7'),
	(15381, 7, 0, 'Before I leave this place, I make one final offreing to you, Lord Staghelm. Should a time arise in which you must gain entry to this accursed fortress, use the Scepter of the Shifting Sands on the sacred gong. The magic holding the barrier together will dissipate and the horrors of Ahn\'Qiraj will be unleashed upon the world once more.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_8'),
	(15381, 8, 0, 'Lord Staghelm, where are you going? You would shatter our bond for the sake of pride?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_9'),
	(15381, 9, 0, 'And now you know all that there is to know, mortal...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_SAY_10'),
	(15381, 10, 0, 'hands the Scepter of the Shifting Sands to Fandral Staghelm.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_EMOTE_1'),
	(15381, 11, 0, 'shakes his head in dissapointment.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_EMOTE_2'),
	(15381, 12, 0, 'kneels down to pick up the fragments of the shattered scepter.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ANACHRONOS_EMOTE_3'),
	(15382, 0, 0, 'My forces cannot overcome the Qiraji defenses. We will not be able to get close enough to place your precious barrier, dragon.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_SAY_1'),
	(15382, 1, 0, 'It is done dragon. Lead the way...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_SAY_2'),
	(15382, 2, 0, 'Ancient ones guide my hand... Wake from your slumber! WAKE AND SEAL THIS CURSED PLACE!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_SAY_3'),
	(15382, 3, 0, 'After the savagery that my people have witnessed and felt, you expect me to accept another burden, dragon? Surely you are mad.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_SAY_4'),
	(15382, 4, 0, 'I want nothing to do with Silithus, the Qiraji and least of all, any damned dragons!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_SAY_5'),
	(15382, 5, 0, 'My son\'s soul will find no comfort in this hollow victory, dragon. I will have him back.Thought it takes a millennia, I WILL have my son back!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_SAY_6'),
	(15382, 6, 0, 'falls to one knee - exhausted.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_EMOTE_1'),
	(15382, 7, 0, 'hurls the Scepter of the Shifting Sands into the barrier, shattering it.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient FANDRAL_EMOTE_2'),
	(15379, 0, 0, 'Aye, Fandral, remember these words: Let not your grief guide your faith. These thoughts you hold... dark places you go, night elf. Absolution cannot be had through misguided vengeance.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient CAELESTRASZ_SAY_1'),
	(15379, 1, 0, 'Do not forget the sacrifices made on this day, night elf. We have all suffered immensely at the hands of these beasts.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient CAELESTRASZ_SAY_2'),
	(15379, 2, 0, 'Alexstrasza grant me the resolve to drive our enemies back!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient CAELESTRASZ_YELL_1'),
	(15380, 0, 0, 'This distraction will give you and the young druid time enough to seal the gate. Do not falter. Now, let us see how they deal with chaotic magic.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ARYGOS_SAY_1'),
	(15380, 1, 0, 'Let them feel the wrath of the Blue Flight! May Malygos protect me!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ARYGOS_YELL_1'),
	(15380, 2, 0, 'nods knowingly.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient ARYGOS_EMOTE_1'),
	(15378, 0, 0, 'There is a way...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient MERITHRA_SAY_1'),
	(15378, 1, 0, 'We will push them back, Anachronos. This I vow. Uphold the end of this task. Let not your hands falter as you seal our fates behind the barrier.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient MERITHRA_SAY_2'),
	(15378, 2, 0, 'Succumb to the endless dream, little ones. Let it consume you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient MERITHRA_YELL_1'),
	(15378, 3, 0, 'glances at her compatriots.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'anachronos the ancient MERITHRA_EMOTE_1'),
